description:
Roles & Responsibilities
We are looking to speak to DevOps Engineers!

Responsibilities
Participate to the automation of the deployment solution.
Build, release, and deploy the platform on top of Jupyter Lab and Jupyter Hub;
Monitor the health of the platform and plan its capacity;
Secure the platform to prevent security breaches or unintended usage;
Tailor the platform to support evolving customer needs.
Monitor the results and quality of the different software solutions and projects implemented in the organisation
Ensure continuous improvement and maintenance of the CI-CD pipeline.

Requirements
Proficient in Linux, Docker, Kubernetes and Helm charts;
Good experience with shell-scripting;
Good experience with Git, ideally with Gitlab;
Good experience with Continuous Delivery, ideally with ArgoCD;
Good experience with Monitoring, ideally with Grafana;
Hands-on experience with Python or a similar programming language.

"Sanderson-iKas" is the brand name for iKas International (Asia) Pte Ltd, a company incorporated in Singapore under Company UEN No.: 200914065E with EA license number 16S8086.
Website: www.sanderson-ikas.sg
